<HEADLINE>
<P>
POWER HAIR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
We need a little public silliness in this age of decline and dismay. 
</P>
<P>
"Power Hair Do's and Don'ts" (Looks, by Karen Grisby Bates, Oct. 14) supplied 
it. 
</P>
<P>
With all the cynicism around us, it's a comfort to come across such wide-eyed 
blither. May I suggest a follow-up article on "Trend-Setting Bellybuttons"? 
</P>
<P>
WM. C. MONTGOMERY 
</P>
<P>
Long Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, COLOR, Arsenio Hall 
</P>
