she married in 1954. Daniel Peebles; Photo, Krantz, second from left, plugging 
"Scruples" on Merv Griffin's talk show. Michael LeRoy; Photo, In Paris in 1949, 
Krantz, center, supervised fashion shoots for hat designers. ; Photo, Krantz, 
dressed for the hoop-rolling contest at Wellesley. 
</P>
