<HEADLINE>
<P>
INDIA TESTS MISSILE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NEW DELHI 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
India has successfully test-fired an advanced anti-tank missile that designers 
say can pierce any known armor, news reports said last week. 
</P>
