<TEXT>
<P>
Dare we be encouraged? Is it wise to embrace the knowledge that San Diego's 
legal profession can boast at least one attorney who questions Dan Broderick's 
duality, and the San Diego County Bar Assn.'s fund drive in Broderick's honor? 
("San Diego at Large," Nov. 28) 
