Wooden Center. In the semifinals Friday night, beginning at 6:30, UCLA will 
face New Mexico (22-6), a winner over Pepperdine Friday, followed by Stanford 
(26-3) against San Diego State (24-11). The title game will be Saturday night 
at 7:30. 
