<HEADLINE>
<P>
LOW DOWN PAYMENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bruss' article with its get-rich-quick overtone is great. However, the eagle 
has landed (i.e. nationwide real estate recession). 
</P>
<P>
Whatever happened to the free and clear American dream? Your article and 
millions of people who believe in this theory are now the new co-stars of 
1990's "American Nightmare." 
</P>
<P>
Bruss states, "home buyers should avoid personal liability on their mortgage, 
just in case property values decline." Brilliant! JAMES D. LEUR 
</P>
<P>
Avalon 
