<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH SURELOCK; 
</P>
<P>
THE SILICON SLEUTH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Once again, SURELOCK's penchant for exactas instead of straight bets on his 
choices cost him a nice payoff. Big Warning, his pick in the ninth Saturday, 
paid $14.60, but the computer lost $90 because it couldn't come up with the 
place horse. 
</P>
<P>
SURELOCK's bets for today are $100 to win on Plenty Of Grace, a $40 exacta, 
Plenty Of Grace to Royal Touch, and a $20 exacta reversing the two in the 
eighth race. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
SURELOCK's Sat. Bankroll: $1,4444 
</P>
<P>
Saturday's Loss: $90 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll: $1,354 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Bob Mieszerski lost $60 when his key exacta horse finished ninth in the fourth 
race. Bob's bet for today is $100 to win on My Boy Adam in the fifth race. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
