Libraries: Need older adult volunteers for the Grandparents and Books program 
to read stories to children two to 10 hours per week. Northridge Library 
information: (818) 866-3640. Sun Valley Library information: (818) 764-7907. 
Sylmar Library information: (818) 367-6102. 
</P>
<P>
Child Advocates Office of the Superior Court: Needs volunteers to work in the 
juvenile dependency court in Van Nuys and downtown Los Angeles. Information: 
(213) 974-5375. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Student Services 
</P>
<P>
